Name: Break It
About the game: Break It is a new stick game where the player control one, or more, stick to hit the ball used to break the pieces on the scenario. You will find pieces with different hits to be breaked. In the scenarios you can find bombs, portals, enemies and more. It's more than 70 levels to be breaked in 8 different scenarios.
